snippet.title: nkdAgility Healthgrades Interview Dave Frisch
snippet.description: I trained over 150 people at Healthgrades and not everyone liked the idea at the beginning. Dave was very opposed to training everyone, so opposed that he took the organised out to dinner to try and get both his team, and himself, out of it. See how he got on...
